# TWRP Recovery Changelog (renoir)

## [3.7.1_12] - 2026-06-13
- **MTP Fixed**: Implemented "Perfect Match" USB logic with official Product IDs (0xFF40/0xFF48) and UDC controller fixes.
- **Vibration Fixed**: Restored stable haptics driver logic for reliable tactile feedback.
- **UI Offsets**: Optimized status bar layout to clear the notch (Y=28, H=6, X=10).
- **CPU Temperature**: Added independent horizontal positioning for CPU temp (150px offset).
- **Backup Improvements**: Added full support for EFS (IMEI/Signal) and Persist partition backups.
- **NTFS Support**: Added ntfs-3g modules for mounting/formatting NTFS USB-OTG drives.
- **Build Automation**: Added a root-aware build.sh script for easy, one-command compilation.
- **Clean Configuration**: Disabled EDL mode and removed redundant/conflicting system properties



